   ↓ considerate, considerable 的辨析 ↓    

----------------------------------------

considerate >> 考虑周到的，体谅的。如：It was considerate of you not to trouble us.(你真体贴人，不打扰我们。)

considerable >> 相当多的，可观的。如：He met a considerable amount of trouble.(他遇到了许多麻烦。)

